definitions.definition: A place in the United Kingdom :

subdefinitions.definition: A suburb of Twickenham in the borough of Richmond upon Thames , Greater London ( OS grid ref TQ1473 ) .
A northern suburb of Ipswich , Suffolk , England ( OS grid ref TM1447 ) .
A small civil parish (served by Claydon and Whitton Parish Council) in Mid Suffolk district, Suffolk , north of the suburb in Ipswich .
A village in Stillington and Whitton parish, Stockton-on-Tees borough , County Durham , England ( OS grid ref NZ3822 ) .
A hamlet in Leintwardine parish, Herefordshire , England ( OS grid ref SO4174 ) .
A village and civil parish in North Lincolnshire district, Lincolnshire , England ( OS grid ref SE9024 ) .
A hamlet and civil parish (without a council) in south Shropshire , England ( OS grid ref SO5772 ) .
A small village and community south of Knighton , Powys , Wales ( OS grid ref SO2767 ) .

definitions.definition: A habitational surname from Old English .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) A place in the United Kingdom :
